Executive Summary

This week, OSAC advanced multi-tenancy foundations and networking
architecture. The team demonstrated project management APIs using Keycloak
organizations for authorization hierarchies, and showcased VLAN-based
tenant isolation through the new networking backend. Key technical
discussions focused on extending the Public IP API for cross-service use
and exploring a generic catalog architecture for improved resource
consistency.

